      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·頌·魯頌·002.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">有駜.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>有駜有駜，駜彼乘黃。夙夜在公，在公明明。
振振鷺，鷺于下。鼓咽咽，醉言舞。于胥樂兮。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Fat and strong, fat and strong,
Fat and strong, are the chestnut teams.
Early and late are the officers in the court,
In the court, discriminating and intelligent.
They are as a flock of egrets on the wing,
Of egrets anon lighting on the ground.
The drums emit their deep sound;
They drink to the full and then dance; --
Thus rejoicing together.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__song-lusong-002__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
