      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·頌·魯頌·002.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">有駜.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>有駜有駜，駜彼乘駽。夙夜在公，在公載燕。
自今以始，歲其有。君子有穀，詒孫子。于胥樂兮。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Fat and strong, fat and strong,
Fat and strong are the teams of iron-greys.
Early and late are the officers with the prince,
With the prince feasting.
From this time forth,
May the years be abundant.
May our prince maintain his goodness,
And transmit it to his descendants! '--
Thus they rejoice together.</seg>
      </tuv>
